title.narrative: Maternal and Newborn Health Technical Resource Facility (TRF)

description.narrative: This activity (Maternal and Newborn Health Technical Resource Facility (TRF)) is a component of Maternal and Newborn Health reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £10,465,851. This component benefits Pakistan, and works in the following sector(s): Medical research, Basic health care, Health education, Health personnel development, Reproductive health care. , with the following implementing partners: British Council, Crown Agents Limited, Ernst & Young Pakistan, Mott MacDonald Limited, PwC, THIRD PARTY MONIES. The start date is 19-01-2009 and the end date is 18-02-2015.
